they can do your SEO,

12:25.490 --> 12:27.860 align:middle line:84%
you're probably,
particularly as a start-up,

12:27.860 --> 12:30.110 align:middle line:90%
you're this important to them.

12:30.110 --> 12:33.110 align:middle line:84%
So you're not going to get
the continuous improvement

12:33.110 --> 12:34.460 align:middle line:90%
process that you need.

12:34.460 --> 12:36.770 align:middle line:84%
And so you, as the
entrepreneur, you,

12:36.770 --> 12:40.280 align:middle line:84%
as the CEO of your company,
have to stay on top of it

12:40.280 --> 12:43.400 align:middle line:84%
because anything that falls
into that category of key

12:43.400 --> 12:46.190 align:middle line:84%
to your success,
you better know it.

12:46.190 --> 12:50.060 align:middle line:84%
You've got to know it, live it,
eat it, sleep it, breathe it.

